comments: Mr. Higa is an AMAZING professor! He is very understanding and respectful. His lectures are good and he uses good examples to help you understand the materials. Show up to class and you will for sure pass the class. He does have quizzes and some papers to do but it isn\'t hard if you know the material. Always available to help outside of class.

comments: Quizzes every other week and knows his stuff about social work. He\'s a nice, funny guy that\'s easy to relate to and is a very understanding, flexible person. We were assigned a final 10 page paper that seems intimidating at first, but Mr. Higa is always willing to help you along the way. Recommend him 10/10.
